Stir by Ingredient Value.

This recipe demonstrates stirring the bowl by an ingredient's value.

Ingredients.
1 g first
2 g second
3 g third
2 g stir_amount

Method.
Put first into mixing bowl.
Put second into mixing bowl.
Put third into mixing bowl.
Stir stir_amount into the mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
